# TEXT-TO-SPEECH (TTS) CONFIGURATION [cite: 35, 42]
VITE_TTS_API_KEY=By75sYyrPgd7pqOjMaXPmQGHoGyUqdGEegzF3QSlalmpr6T1zF6JJQQJ99CCACfhMk5XJ3w3AAAAACOGzx69
VITE_TTS_API_ENDPOINT=https://swedencentral.tts.speech.microsoft.com/cognitiveservices/v1

# SPEECH-TO-TEXT (STT) CONFIGURATION [cite: 34, 41]
